{
  "title": "Tamasusuusuane ki kadaengane",
  "titleCh": "魯凱族的土地倫理",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "土地倫理在魯凱族的部落是一項非常重要的，凡是不能遵照這個倫理的，必引起兄弟、親戚、部落人之間的紛擾，尤其是部落之間常因而打戰，造成傷亡。所以一定有立約來遵行，不去移動界標。老年人非常清楚這個土地的規範，尤其是在還沒有土地所有權狀之前。然而現在已經有了規範之後，反而限制了頭目對土地的權力，無論是獵區、河川、耕作地、林地、和水源地等都已經取得土地所有權狀了。",
      "ab": "Kay suusuane ki kadaengane tinumakucingalrane turamuru ikay ki sanakacekele, sanakaipasuusu kudra ki tamasususuane ki kadaengane lini, wadawlu ku amakakarivuane ku mababetake ku malritudrane ku mararetese ku masakacekele, saniange kikay lacekele amani ku makarururuburu maravaravase pakela ku mapacapacay, ngualay ki tapauangatungatuane, tapawtaletalekane, taaciladhane. Ai, tarasingiakay ki tamasuusuane ki cekele, ala ngiesaynga ka inianenga. \r\n[===]\r\nPakay ku akalakebane si kaikikabebetethe kay kadaengane, tuataulrisisiane kudra ki matiasamilringi ku drakerale, \r\nkudra ki angatungatu turamuru, kaiwamuamua ralabe, velevele, tuumauma, ikaykay tumanenga kidruanga, sapapacay, tuataulrisiane madu amia, lakatayngeane ka sapaukukuludrane ki laumaumase, kudra kaikaamuane cacapange si kiucuugu lakacaeme, pangilisi, manuela ku tacekecekelane, lakamani ku tutawlrisiane lini. Malrigili turamuru kay sidrumane sasuusuane arakay marasikay pakialibake ki kadaengane.",
      "order": "1",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/25/280aabcd8c22f9b42b3e04022a4ca979.wav",
