    {
      "chinese": "所以一定要立約來遵行，不逾越界線，老年人非常清楚這個土地的規範，尤其是在還沒有土地所有權之前。然而現在有了立法規範後，反而限制了頭目對土地的權力，無論是獵區、河川或耕作地，都已經取得土地所有權狀了，造林地、旱地、水源地等也是。",
      "ab": "Lakamani ku tarapikay kudra amasingikaikaiyane si kaimadrikidrikisi, kaipasilribate kudra ki saagisane ki paagiagisane, wathingale kay tarudrawdrange turamuru kay ki tamasususuane ki kadaengane, saniange sakakadruana ku pacase ki kadaengane. \r\n[===]\r\nAi, kikaynga kiatuhulricenga kay kadaengane si kakadruanga ku angisasingikayyane ki talialaalay ki cekele miaku nadruma, kay taalupane, kay drakerale, kay tatuumaumane. Wamalranga kudra nitukiane ikay ki taramarasikaikaiyane ki kadaengane si daedae ki tatudadaanane.",
